query: SELECT ?item WHERE {BIND(wd:Q158056 as ?item). ?item wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q5. hint:Prior hint:gearing "forward".}

SELECT DISTINCT ?Month_brut ?Month_Name ?Year (sample(?patronageP3872) as ?patronage)   (SAMPLE(?reference_URL) AS ?sample_reference_URL)
WHERE
{    ?item wdt:P238 ?airport_code
VALUES ?airport_code    {
 "CPT"    }
    ?item p:P3872 ?statement.
    VALUES ?rank { wikibase:NormalRank wikibase:PreferredRank } 
?statement wikibase:rank ?rank.
  ?statement ps:P3872 ?patronageP3872.
  ?statement pqv:P585 ?timevalue.
  OPTIONAL { ?statement prov:wasDerivedFrom / (pr:P854|pr:P4656) ?reference_URL. }
  ?timevalue wikibase:timeValue ?time.
  ?timevalue wikibase:timePrecision 10 . # Precision only month (10)
  BIND (MONTH(?time) AS ?month)
  BIND (YEAR(?time) AS ?Year)
  VALUES (?Month_brut  ?Month_Name)  { (1 "jan") 
                                  (2 "fév" ) 
                                  (3 "mar" )  
                                  (4 "avr" ) 
                                   (5 "mai" ) 
                                   (6 "juin" ) 
                                   (7 "juil" ) 
                                   (8 "aoû" ) 
                                   (9 "sep" ) 
                                   (10 "oct" ) 
                                   (11 "nov" ) 
                                   (12 "déc" ) 
  }
  filter(?month = ?Month_brut )
filter(?Year>=2018).
    FILTER (?Year < YEAR(NOW())).
} GROUP BY ?Month_brut  ?Month_Name ?Year
ORDER BY ?Year ?Month_brut
